{id global-option-units, orbit heading, h2[Global Option Units]}
Global option units are units with "global" opton. A valid global option unit should be at the beginning of a line of stdn.
[]
'Multiple global option units are supported. In global option units, the value of options like *src and *href can be a urls file.'
[]
{global, level 2, test[]}
{two[
    {display[Source]}
    {display[Result]}
    {lang stdn, code[
        '{global, level 2, test[]}'
        '{id e5, orbit test, equation[{display, \'\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}dx=\frac{\sqrt\pi}2\'}]}'
    ]}
    {div[
        {id e5, orbit test, equation[{display, '\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}dx=\frac{\sqrt\pi}2'}]}
    ]}
]}
